CMS Name: Local Search Strategy ◦ LIMITLESS CHIRO ATX
Project text content 01:
Limitless Chiropractic, an Austin-based chiropractor, had a website that was underperforming in terms of organic search traffic.

Despite having a consistent online presence, their website had reached a traffic ceiling that it couldn't break through. The client needed to improve their website's visibility and attract more qualified leads through search engines.
Project text content 02:
Problem

Limitless Chiropractic, an Austin-based chiropractor, had a website that was underperforming in terms of organic search traffic. Despite having a consistent online presence, their website had reached a traffic ceiling that it couldn't break through. The client needed to improve their website's visibility and attract more qualified leads through search engines.

-----

Solution

As an SEO agency, we were brought in to help Limitless Chiropractic overcome their traffic plateau and drive more organic search visibility. Starting on March 25th, 2024, we implemented a series of technical SEO improvements:

  1. Added redirects to ensure all pages were properly linked and accessible to search engines.
  2. Optimized blog titles and slugs for better keyword targeting.
  3. Set up URL monitoring to track any changes or issues.
  4. Submitted a comprehensive sitemap to Google Search Console.
  5. Added optimized metadata, schema markup, follow/index tags, and social share metadata to each page.
  6. Enabled follow tags and added EN language tag for better indexing.
  7. Implemented Google Tag Manager for improved tracking and analytics.

These optimizations were applied to key pages including the Home, Services, About Us, FAQs, Blog, Contact Us, and individual blog posts.
Project text content 03:
Result

Just over one month into the six-month engagement, Limitless Chiropractic is already seeing significant improvements in their organic search performance. Comparing the period of 3/25/24 - 4/28/24 to the previous period (2/22/24 - 3/25/24), the website achieved:

  • 35.78% increase in total clicks
  • 25.23% increase in total impressions
  • 10.34% increase in average CTR
  • 3 position improvement in average ranking

The website has broken through its previous traffic ceiling and is experiencing a new level of volatility, indicating that it is "waking up" and becoming more visible to search engines.

By focusing on crawlability, indexability, and other key technical SEO factors, we were able to deliver meaningful results for Limitless Chiropractic in a short timeframe. These early improvements have kept the client highly satisfied as we continue our six-month engagement to drive even greater organic search performance for their business.

Project text content 01:
WOLF FIT, a Raleigh-based personal training business specializing in small groups, athletes, and one-on-one training, needed a website that could quickly attract new clients and drive business growth.

As a new venture, WOLF FIT required a strong online presence to establish credibility, showcase their services, and convert website visitors into paying customers.

The lack of a professional website hindered their ability to reach their target audience and scale their business effectively.
Project text content 02:
Solution

To address WOLF FIT's need for a website that could rapidly bring in new business, we proposed building a custom website using Webflow, a powerful no-code web design platform. Our team collaborated closely with WOLF FIT to understand their unique selling proposition, target audience, and business goals. With this insight, we designed and developed a visually striking, user-friendly website that effectively communicated WOLF FIT's brand message and value proposition.

-----

Key features of the website included:

  1. Engaging and informative content that educated visitors about WOLF FIT's personal training services, expertise, and philosophy.
  2. Compelling calls-to-action (CTAs) strategically placed throughout the site to encourage visitors to take action, such as signing up for a free consultation or contacting WOLF FIT directly.
  3. A responsive design that ensured optimal viewing and functionality across all devices, including desktops, tablets, and smartphones.
  4. Seamless integration with third-party tools, such as Google Analytics and a CRM, to track website performance and manage leads effectively.

By leveraging Webflow's capabilities and our team's expertise in web design and development, we were able to deliver a fully functional, high-quality website within just 30 days.
Project text content 03:
Result

The launch of WOLF FIT's new Webflow website had an immediate and significant impact on their business:

  1. Within the first month, website traffic increased by 200%, with a substantial portion of visitors coming from organic search and referral sources.
  2. The website's conversion rate reached 3%, with dozens of potential clients filling out the contact form or calling WOLF FIT directly to inquire about their services.
  3. The increased visibility and credibility provided by the new website allowed WOLF FIT to secure partnerships with local gyms and athletic organizations, further expanding their reach and client base.

By delivering a professional, high-performing website in just 30 days, we helped WOLF FIT establish a strong online presence, attract new clients, and lay the foundation for long-term business growth in the competitive Raleigh personal training market.
